BioText:
Wealth Strategist is a Wealth Planner providing comprehensive wealth planning for Manager clients. She analyzes financial data, and develops and monitors wealth plans targeted to client’s goals and objectives. Areas of expertise include retirement, investments, education, risk management, and estate. Wealth has over 25 years of experience in wealth planning.

Prior to joining Manager Wealth was the Director of Financial Planning at another firm for 13 years where she was responsible for development and maintenance of all financial planning related software features as well as sales and training. Wealth has domain expertise in financial planning software and oversees the day to day management and support of Manager’s technological offering of wealth plans and client deliverables.

Portfolio Manager, CFP®  is a Relationship Manager in Manager’s Philadelphia office. In this role, Mr. Portfolio provides investment advice and manages the portfolios of the Company's affluent individual clients.

Wealth Advisor is a Wealth Administrator in Manager’s Philadelphia office.  In partnership with investment management colleagues, she is responsible for the administrative aspects of trust, investment management, and retirement accounts for Manager’s high-net-worth clients. She provides tailored wealth management advice while ensuring fiduciary business practices fulfill compliance and regulatory requirements.
